text:
Reddit 
Ultra Music Festival has revealed its preliminary lineup for 2017. The EDM mega fest takes place March 24th – 26th at Bayfront Park in Miami, Florida. 
Headliners include Underworld, The Prodigy, Ice Cube, and Justice, who will be debuting a brand new live show. Other acts include Major Lazer, Tiësto, DJ Snake, Steve Aoki, David Guetta, Above and Beyond, Carl Cox, Sasha and John Digweed, Alesso, Afrojack, Armin van Buuren, Hardwell, Dubfire, Axwell^Ingrosso, Dash Berlin, and Tale of Us. 
General admission and VIP passes are now on sale . Artists
